  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/Intents\/INPaymentMethodType\/store\ncrawled: 2025-12-12T05:44:36Z\n---\n\n# INPaymentMethodType.store\n\n**Case**\n\nPayment using a store charge card.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\ncase store\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **INPaymentMethodType.unknown**: An unspecified payment type.\n- **INPaymentMethodType.checking**: Payment from a checking account.\n- **INPaymentMethodType.savings**: Payment from a savings account.\n- **INPaymentMethodType.brokerage**: Payment from a brokerage account.\n- **INPaymentMethodType.debit**: Payment using a debit card.\n- **INPaymentMethodType.credit**: Payment using a credit card.\n- **INPaymentMethodType.prepaid**: Payment using a prepaid card or account.\n- **INPaymentMethodType.applePay**: Payment using Apple Pay.\n\n",
